Welcome to Anhur IMIE [Isolated Malware Investigation Environment].

Anhur was started when a group of guys working in the industry came together to solve a need that is not satisfied anywhere other than in commercial tools - sandboxing.

There have been attempts over the years to create effective sandbox solutions however most are either:

 

a) Paid commercial services which a lot of organisations cannot afford

b) Obsolete with the new requirement for interactive sandbox environments

 

That is where Anhur IMIE comes in. 

 

Anhur means 'Slayer of Enemies', true to form Anhur will slay your adversaries malware using a combination of both great tools; Elasticsearch and Suricata NIDS, Anhur was developed by Based DFIR team.

 

To begin, simply select one of the Analysis VM's from the top navigation bar and hit connect once there. 

 

Thanks for installing and using Anhur. We hope you enjoy it. Any feedback is appreciated @ github.com/basedfir
